===Transitive Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-sibilant|scrat|ch|}}

# To [[rub]] a [[surface]] with a [[sharp]] object, especially by a living [[creature]] to [[remove]] [[itch]]ing with [[nail]]s, [[claw]]s, etc.
